OL,3,CPoliticians 'tone-deaf' as taxpayers'
OL,4,C#35,000 spent on foreign trips
OL,6,FMore than #35,000 was spent on the
OL,7,Fhotel and travel expenses of Jersey
OL,8,Fpoliticians attending Commonwealth
OL,9,FParliamentary Association (CPA) events
OL,10,Fabroad in 2023.
OL,12,FAn ITV News Freedom of Information
OL,13,Frequest has revealed there were six
OL,14,FCPA trips during the year, totalling
OL,15,F#35,019.76.
OL,17,FThe most expensive was the 66th
OL,18,FCommonwealth Parliamentary Conference
OL,19,Fin Ghana which three politicians and
OL,20,Fthe States Greffier attended, costing
OL,21,Fnearly #12,000.
