OL,3,CPoliticians 'tone-deaf' as taxpayers'
OL,4,C#35,000 spent on foreign trips
OL,6,FOther travel included the 52nd British
OL,7,FIslands and Mediterranean Regional
OL,8,FConference in London, an "advanced
OL,9,Fprofessional development and skills-
OL,10,Fbuilding residency programme" in
OL,11,FCanada, and a workshop entitled
OL,12,F"Strengthening Parliament Action to
OL,13,FAddress Modern Slavery and Human
OL,14,FTrafficking in Supply Chains" in Kenya.
OL,16,FThe #35,000 bill also included around
OL,17,F#8,000 on a "bespoke programme of
OL,18,Fevents in Westminster created by the
OL,19,FCPA UK" for 11 Jersey politicians,
OL,20,Fmostly backbenchers, from 16 to 19 May
OL,21,F2023.
