OL,4,C#35,000 spent on foreign trips
OL,6,FDeputy Max Andrews said: "I think it
OL,7,Fshould only be for senior politicians
OL,8,Fso that is politicians in the
OL,9,Fexecutive, but I think for
OL,10,Fbackbenchers there isn't really any
OL,11,Freason to go away because we have a
OL,12,Fduty to serve our constituents and
OL,13,Fthat means we've got to be based in
OL,14,Fthe island full-time."
OL,16,FHowever, Guernsey Deputy John Gollop
OL,17,Fhas defended the spending.
