OL,6,FHe explained: "Guernsey and Jersey are
OL,7,Fnot Basingstoke or Wakefield or places
OL,8,Fin England and I think every time the
OL,9,FChannel Islands sends people to
OL,10,Fimportant conferences, it's usually
OL,11,Fmoney well spent.
OL,13,F"It's about public relations but it's
OL,14,Fmore than that, it's also about
OL,15,Fnegotiations, an ambassadorial role."
